        [
          "老師：下禮拜三（五月十二）是阮阿媽八十歲生日，阮阿爸卜[毛^火]阮歸家伙仔轉去庄跤，共阿媽做生日，所以我五月十二想卜共老師請一日仔假，迄日个功課，我會佇厝裡自修，袂耽誤著，希望老師准假。",
          "Lau7-su1: E7 le2-pai3-sann1 (goo7-geh8 tsap8-ji7) si7 guan2 a1-ma2 peh4-tsap8 hue3 senn1-jit8, guan2 a1-pa1 beh4 tshua7 guan2 kui1-ke1-hue2-a2 tng2 khi3 tsng1-kha1, ka7 a1-ma2 tso3-senn1-jit8, soo2-i2 gua2 goo7-gueh8 tsap8-ji7 siunn7-beh4 ka7 lau7-su1 tshiann2 tsit8 jit8 a2 ka2, hit4 jit8 e5 kong1-kho3, gua2 e7 ti7 tshu3--lih tsu7-siu1, be7 tam1-goo7 tioh8, hi1-bang7 lau7-su1 tsun2 ka2."
        ]
      ],
